# PR-first parallel workflow enforcement

1. Default every non-trivial slice to **PR-oriented execution**:
   - shape changes into reviewable units,
   - preserve concise validation evidence,
   - keep branch/commit flow compatible with `gh pr create`.
   - Long autonomous loops: [CURSOR_AUTONOMOUS_LOOP_AND_PR_WORKFLOW_SSOT.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/CURSOR_AUTONOMOUS_LOOP_AND_PR_WORKFLOW_SSOT.md) + [cursor-grok-agent-hierarchy-and-loops.mdc](cursor-grok-agent-hierarchy-and-loops.mdc).

2. For work that can parallelize safely, prefer Cursor **3.3+ / 3.11+** primitives:
   - **Build in Parallel** and `/multitask` for independent lanes,
   - **side chats** (`/side`, `/btw`) for read-heavy tangents while main agent continues,
   - keep dependent steps serialized.

3. Background automation must run through **host-managed** schedulers and never compete with foreground interactivity:
   - **macOS (M5/carmel):** `launchd`, `macos-run-background-program-tasks.sh`, [`install-background-runner-launchagent.sh`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/scripts/install-background-runner-launchagent.sh)
   - **RHEL 10.x (Intel/horeb):** user **`systemd`** timers/services ([`config/systemd/background-task-health.timer`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/config/systemd/background-task-health.timer)), `./scripts/run-background-program-tasks.sh` with **`BG_LOCK_CONFLICT_EXIT_OK=1`**
   - foreground pressure gets priority on both hosts; background heavy lanes self-throttle using dynamic guard signals ([`BACKGROUND_TASK_AUTOMATION_SSOT.md`](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/BACKGROUND_TASK_AUTOMATION_SSOT.md))

4. Do not introduce ad-hoc duplicate background owners:
   - keep single-owner lock semantics enabled,
   - document any override in SSOT status rows.

5. Every PR-workflow policy change must update SSOT docs in the same slice:
   - `CONTINUE_ENGINEERING_PLAYBOOK_SSOT.md`
   - `BACKGROUND_TASK_AUTOMATION_SSOT.md`
   - `FOREGROUND_BACKGROUND_TASK_CONTROL_PLANE_SSOT.md`
   - `COMPREHENSIVE_PROJECT_STATUS_REPORT.md` and `CHANGELOG.md`
